wikipedia_page.main: Leomie Jasmin Francis Anderson (born 14 February 1993) is a British model, fashion designer, and activist. She has walked in four consecutive Victoria's Secret Fashion Shows from 2015 to 2018, and became a Victoria's Secret Angel in 2019. Anderson was featured in 2020's Forbes '30 Under 30' list within the Art & Culture category.

response: Naomi Campbell was the first black model to appear on the front cover of Time, French Vogue, and the September issue of American Vogue. Other notable models include Leomie Anderson, Jourdan Dunn, Paloma Elsesser and Munroe Bergdorf.
